org.ica.utilityClasses

Class ObjectFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ica.utilityClasses.ObjectFactory

  • public final class ObjectFactory
extends java.lang.Object
    This class is responsible for instantiating and holding references to most of the objects manipulated by the program.

    Salim AHMED
